list.item:
That the National Constitution of 1886, in incision [paragraph] No. 1 of Article 202, says also that the properties
                            which formerly belonged to the Colombian Union now belong to the
                            Republic;

That by Decree No. 1320, of November 28, 1914, the Executive Power
                            decided that statistics in regard to mining properties should be
                            compiled, and determined the manner in which this should be done;
